{"tid":351042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[An/I]在地下城尋求怪物祭二回","createTime":"2017-08-07T16:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T05:17:24.000Z","uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb73c4ee4b5fa0efc13047f4f421540445fccbeb","tid":351042,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"遊戲官網:<a href=\"http://danmemo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdanmemo.com%2F&d=mTU0DgY%2Bj%2F4NPX0nv9Bh%2BI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8bfc50c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://danmemo.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/VIKxroQbo1--RYYnQhs1lxT3MLoyEXcUw9PVvLYsAQ0ChhbpeNEDVGhjMj0iq3yY2iI=h900-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FVIKxroQbo1--RYYnQhs1lxT3MLoyEXcUw9PVvLYsAQ0ChhbpeNEDVGhjMj0iq3yY2iI%3Dh900-rw&h=ad40d2c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51OklbzfFdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D51OklbzfFdA&d=mTU0DgY%2Bj%2F4NPX0nv9Bh%2BI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b20b548d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51OklbzfFdA</a><br />\n<br />\nIos:<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/%E3%83%80%E3%83%B3%E3%81%BE%E3%81%A1-%E3%83%A1%E3%83%A2%E3%83%AA%E3%82%A2-%E3%83%95%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E3%82%BC/id1220768220?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2F%25E3%2583%2580%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2581%25BE%25E3%2581%25A1-%25E3%2583%25A1%25E3%2583%25A2%25E3%2583%25AA%25E3%2582%25A2-%25E3%2583%2595%25E3%2583%25AC%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2582%25BC%2Fid1220768220%3Fmt%3D8%26ign-mpt%3Duo%253D4&d=mTU0DgY%2Bj%2F4NPX0nv9Bh%2BI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d6613d9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/%E3%83%80%E3%83%B3%E3%81%BE%E3%81%A1-%E3%83%A1%E3%83%A2%E3%83%AA%E3%82%A2-%E3%83%95%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E3%82%BC/id1220768220?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4</a><br />\nAn:<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.danmemo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.danmemo&d=mTU0DgY%2Bj%2F4NPX0nv9Bh%2BI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fe660992\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.danmemo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<br />\nQ:邊隻起手最好?<br />\nA:奶媽(里維莉亞)/劍姬<br />\n<br />\nQ:SUPPORT有咩用?<br />\nA:幫手加能力值同被動技<br />\n<br />\nQ:唔夠打恩惠HARD升唔到人點算?<br />\nA:升3星打/升SUPPORT<br />\n<br />\nQ:主線去到幾多話?<br />\nA:29話<br />\n<br />\nQ:3星同4星有咩分別?<br />\nA:4星能力高少少,大絕唔同,BUFF技幅度都有唔同<br />\n<br />\nQ:器有咩用?<br />\nA:爆擊&amp;反擊<br />\n<br />\nQ:點解升唔到最底果粒恩惠?<br />\nA:要爆熟練同點滿全頁恩惠<br />\n<br />\nQ:7日果張卷係咪可以揀4星?<br />\nA:只可以抽4星,揀4星果張要課金<br />\n<br />\nQ:唔夠體打關點算？<br />\nA:用哂D道具回AP, 之後爆石，10AP回一次，如果你KEEP住拎S,應該D石一路用一路越來越多<br />\n<br />\nQ: 1*男主角有5絆，升唔升好？<br />\nA: 你可以試下，不過遲早一定會飛走，但點都要放佢入隊，後備都得，因為拎S條件係要有佢係隊<br />\n<br />\nQ: 鬥技場同武器係乜？<br />\nA: 未岀，待更新<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣升星？<br />\nA: 滿LV後將D恩惠升哂佢，咁就可以升，最多升到6星<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣突破？<br />\nA: 6*升滿恩惠，再有絆就得？<br />\n<br />\nQ: 乜野係絆？點先有？<br />\nA: 抽到一樣嘅英就會變成絆<br />\n<br />\nQ: 乜野係白聖石？點有？<br />\nA: 賣絆，白聖石可以用黎換道具，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">包括3*券</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等巴打幫手補完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ff7b91e9557ef1faecd93c038ab5ebf7982e8c","tid":351042,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:06:23.000Z","msg":"新手留名"},{"pid":"2cf60f85d536d83a0e4dcc1643badcf74cb20939","tid":351042,"uid":90336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T19:05:37.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c631f48bbbb91aedf9ed59f8fce5e54c123b3fa","tid":351042,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T20:48:59.000Z","msg":"抽到浴衣命 有無用"},{"pid":