lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 無課金</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/110238_e9d26932957b267f4260049e980c60b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F110238_e9d26932957b267f4260049e980c60b2.jpg&h=38824f01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/110238_e791184a0cb0cc419ad9445491620d12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F110238_e791184a0cb0cc419ad9445491620d12.jpg&h=f238a48e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/110241_093db431fc787cc4d7c47c86bac44bbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F110241_093db431fc787cc4d7c47c86bac44bbd.jpg&h=e9f24629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁算唔算好 想知各位巴打情況 指教一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 無課金</blockquote><br />\n10抽咗幾多次?<br />\n浴衣男豬好似2-3突先有明顯輸出<br />\n劍姬唔洗講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4星坦我都百抽都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，後期明顯喺要隻坦嚟頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未有4星媽媽莉莉前用3星千草好D(記得活動刷到拎到5絆)<br />\n(利申，有4星1突媽媽同4星0突莉莉都照5突千草，因為有魔防BUFF)<br />\nSUP方面我得一開頭送隻4星都玩到，你有兩隻夠玩嘅<br />\n3星有3隻防封防暈防睡你都有兩隻了<br />\n如果仲刷到石嘅不妨刷多D抽下媽媽女神UP池<br />\n抽多D先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0073795ccf0270c7038634d5a8ae1ae034f3f5fb","tid":351042,"uid":107255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/110238_e9d26932957b267f4260049e980c60b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F110238_e9d26932957b267f4260049e980c60b2